{"tid":1761952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥指香港處於困難時期　她與政府正聆聽市民聲音","createTime":"2019-11-29T08:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T11:09:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":480,"uniUserReply":141,"replies":[{"pid":"88be069dd8691333d347dffb7d07dba22ae9ec79","tid":1761952,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"到訪曼谷的行政長官林鄭月娥，與泰國政府簽訂加強經濟合作的諒解備忘錄。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥形容，香港正處於困難時期，儘管社會動盪，她仍然想向泰國的朋友保證，香港的根基，包括一國兩制下的獨特優勢、法治及司法獨立，仍然健全，她與她的政府正聆聽市民聲音，期望以對話化解香港一些深層次問題，她堅信香港能夠與以往一樣恢復過來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1495142_1_20191129151557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1495142_1_20191129151557.jpg&h=968d19fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495142-20191129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495142-20191129.htm&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=8a026a7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495142-20191129.htm&h=ada78e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495142-20191129.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n佢真係好無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8737b83be25d3a46c95353320347e39ca775a0a","tid":1761952,"uid":288979,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"即係佢又要出手了搞示威者了"},{"pid":"9300e559168c78d80a6ee98941ec141abd398122","tid":1761952,"uid":4942,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"聆你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48d1842ef35715a86b31fcb843b7c43e4f99e80","tid":1761952,"uid":288523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4f2ee9ce638d2